Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:37.81,up,NTP,0,0,0,,作为初音岛上重要的旅游资源的樱花树突然间凋零了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:41.65,up,NTP,0,0,0,,为众人所熟知的赏花名胜 樱花公园也正如现在大家所见一般
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.90,up,NTP,0,0,0,,此现象现今仍呈现进一步扩散趋势
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:47.78,up,NTP,0,0,0,,给当地的观光产业造成了巨大影响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.74,0:02:54.21,up,NTP,0,0,0,,今天观光协会早已召开会议拟订相关对策
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.39,up,NTP,0,0,0,,不过就现在仍处于束手无策的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:03:00.26,up,NTP,0,0,0,,并分成了坚持调查樱花树凋零原因的解谜派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:02.71,up,NTP,0,0,0,,以及探寻其他可开发利用资源的摸索派两派
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.95,up,NTP,0,0,0,,会议曾一度陷入了混乱局面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.35,up,NTP,0,0,0,,关于导致樱花凋零的因果关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.82,up,NTP,0,0,0,,相关部门正从近邻的居民那里收集目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:17.38,up,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年前曾出现过的不会凋零的樱花树也发生过凋零的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:20.37,up,NTP,0,0,0,,并在十年前左右突然复活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:24.94,up,NTP,0,0,0,,即是说 这次的这一现象 虽然原因暂时不明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:28.16,up,NTP,0,0,0,,不过继续这样发展下去 初音岛上所有的樱花凋零也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,----TEXT----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.43,0:00:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没消失…？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实是应该…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道… 是场梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.33,0:02:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 凋零了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.12,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是造成大骚动了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岛上的人们看上很不安呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经出门了 说是学生会有事要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.58,0:02:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没办法呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个煎鸡蛋真好吃呢 下次也教我怎么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什 什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,煎鸡蛋真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个岛一直做着的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.39,0:03:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.08,0:04:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姬学姐那边没问题了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 我昨天早退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已经解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来真是让人大吃一惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.49,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花树竟突然凋零了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯 来学校的路上看到的枯树也很多呢 总觉得好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.68,0:04:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们已经习惯了盛开的樱花树呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.47,0:04:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得有点寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是趁现在尽兴地去赏次花什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须解开这一谜团才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是温室效应造成的吗 或者是地磁的颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.23,0:04:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛 既然凋零了那也没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说了比起这种事情 我更担心下节课的数学考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.94,0:04:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考试？什么考试？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏 你忘了吗？ 今天有数学的随堂考试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 这可不行啊 我怎么这么粗心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:04:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不像雪村的作风啊 你引以为荣的记忆力怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说是一时疏忽啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这样我的战友就增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.08,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑 现在开始复习也足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样啊 我们一起接受补习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 杏是因为忘了有考试…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是樱花树的力量消失了的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终我也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.71,0:05:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了 音姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 音姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.65,0:05:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你认识他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是这么回事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后大哥就火了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我会从大家的记忆中逐渐消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都将会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后看着弟弟君 也不会记起他是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着他也什么都想不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天总会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在不久的将来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.62,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也太残酷了 弟弟君明明什么都没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.25,0:07:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是我的错 对不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之 今天去哪吃？ 学生食堂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊不 今天我带了便当…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.79,0:07:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃便当吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不记得有答应过你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.70,0:07:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛 一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 你个恋爱土豪 真是让人羡慕啊 好家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你误会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事啦 学生食堂乃是孤身一人的家伙们聚集的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然便当就该在外面吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 好像有点冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:59.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 你好坏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样也就不会觉得冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.62,0:08:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也做便当给你吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 你想谋杀我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会练习的啦 我也想让你说一次我做的便当很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那会是哪年哪月呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会进行特训的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不抓紧点的话 时间上也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说… 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.22,0:08:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 难道我做便当就让你那么不安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的啦 我会好好地练习 绝对会让哥哥你说好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 吃吧吃吧 开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住惯了的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱小姐消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.98,0:09:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后谁都不在了…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.67,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.67,0:10:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.76,0:10:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的话就回答一声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在叫我？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是既没回应 又找不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.31,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起 确实抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为惩罚 早饭至少要做3个菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.36,0:10:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天又先出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 奈奈佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.89,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 义之君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.74,0:10:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起对不起 有点发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈奈佳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这人是我们班的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.03,0:11:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.24,0:11:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,精神不好啊 没睡好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在等你哦 樱内同志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樱花树凋零的原因我想过了 想要听听你的意见…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的朋友果然还是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 别勒那么紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.26,0:11:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是出人意料的举动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.06,0:12:03.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和你们相遇真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之你 吃了什么不干净的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止弟弟君消失的办法…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.43,0:12:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.12,0:12:29.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没上课吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的现代国语是写读书报告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是自修
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们去哥哥家里做火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点事要做 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥很寂寞哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.44,0:12:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 是很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样子 一定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 莫非你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.09,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅 那就我一个人去准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐有空的话也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.16,0:13:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是哪个班的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑到别人班里干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太冒失了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.34,0:14:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人的时候跑到别人的教室
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.11,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经开始问名字了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 有什么奇怪的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店员终于忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只试穿不买呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜你一个人试了60套 做得太过火啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有60套啦 才58套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 两个人在购物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.91,0:14:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么印象呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 是我呀 义之
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说他叫义之 你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.23,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:14:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是搭讪 一定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.78,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时搭讪两个？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是想让一大群可爱女生来侍奉自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他找错人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.29,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有事 不能和你约会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.19,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.50,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说还是蛮帅的 有点浪费了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.33,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.53,0:15:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.15,0:15:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火锅材料买好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.63,0:15:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 肉非常便宜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 真期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.83,0:15:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥你负责切菜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你想让我一个人做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤头我会帮忙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 女孩子拿了那么多东西你没什么感觉的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开口让我拿的话会帮你拿的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 哥哥 今天肉很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天服务真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.48,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.46,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:05.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的话 你不都是掠夺我精心培育的肉的么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 说得真难听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是今天哥哥你的份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的全都是我的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你要稍微自重点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真啰唆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.77,0:17:23.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是火锅好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天也吃火锅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.68,0:17:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后天也继续吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 全火锅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:30.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓的一家人的餐桌文化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太夸张了吧 还不是只有我和你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.96,0:17:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了 虽然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候说这个虽说有点那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起的话 会后悔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.21,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唔 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不愿意和我一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.69,0:18:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样陪着我 我非常高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然非常高兴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是兄妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一起不是理所当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:40.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:42.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会在哥哥身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不会后悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.80,0:19:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就和往常一样 和哥哥一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:10.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都这样 和哥哥一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去学校 一起笑啊吵啊吹吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不是挺好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.26,0:19:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:18.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.05,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.90,0:20:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁 你认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.80,0:20:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不认识…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像… 你没印象吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.06,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.35,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是你以前甩掉的男人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 没有那样的人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样呀 那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没见过那就是陌生人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了月岛 关于吉他手的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样了 找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行不行 完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:21:00.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对高达有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 认错人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.68,0:23:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要说出口的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.48,0:23:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深藏在心中的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.38,0:23:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传达 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.74,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}闇に舞い散る
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:59.77,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}桜の花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:07.33,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}優しい嘘と孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:12.08,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}包み込むように
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.67,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}見つめ合うほど
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:24.06,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}わからなくなるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:28.24,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そばにいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.11,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}それだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.75,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大切な人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:43.13,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想い出が溢れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:47.83,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}柔らかな光景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:55.08,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}静かなる決意に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:01.72,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}枯れないその涙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:10.12,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}この痛みは何処へと
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:16.19,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}願い残し行くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:27.10,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}時は迫り無情に微笑む運命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:33.32,INJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}桜風　ざわめく
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:53.74,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在暗夜中飘散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:59.77,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}樱花之瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:07.33,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}像被善意的谎言与孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.43,0:15:12.08,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}包围着一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:17.67,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}相视越久
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:24.06,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}越会搞不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.67,0:15:28.24,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想伴你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.41,0:15:31.11,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:35.75,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:43.13,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}回忆满溢而出
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:47.83,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}柔和的光景
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:55.08,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}静谧的决意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:01.72,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流不尽的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:10.12,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}这痛楚将何去何从
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:16.19,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你要留下愿望远去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:27.10,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}时间无情地逼近微笑的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:33.32,INCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}樱风 渐起
